title: Helen Clark: Speech at Opening of UNDP Regional Bureau for Asia-Pacific Meeting on UNDP’s role ...
text: ( Source : UNDP - United Nations Development Programme Afghanistan ) 18 Oct 2015 Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia 9.15am, Sunday, It is my pleasure to welcome you all to the Regional Management Meeting of UNDP's Regional Bureau for Asia-Pacific (RBAP).
